    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving engine remains crisp, delivering linear power through its six individual throttle bodies and a precision Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The chassis exhibits the balanced 50/50 weight distribution characteristic of the platform, further enhanced by a factory-spec M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. While showing minor signs of regular use consistent with its age, the mechanical synchronization and throttle response are excellent. This is a mechanically sound example of an M-division icon, ready for the spirited driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
