    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a well-maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle has served as a reliable daily driver and remains in impressive mechanical and cosmetic shape. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small scuff on the rear passenger-side wheel rim. Inside, the cabin is appointed in premium black leather; the seats are firm and comfortable, with only light creasing on the driver-side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic glass roof to the heated steering wheel and the Bose surround-sound system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the 3.0L V6 engine delivers smooth, consistent power, paired with a PDK transmission that shifts flawlessly. I have kept a detailed log of all maintenance, including a recent oil service and a fresh set of cabin filters. The tires are matching Michelins with approximately 60% tread remaining. This Macan offers a perfect entry into Porsche performance with the peace of mind that comes from a documented service history.",
